1
00:00:37,300 --> 00:00:40,580
=Reincarnated Love=

2
00:00:40,780 --> 00:00:43,700
=Episode 22=

3
00:00:50,960 --> 00:00:51,800
Milady,

4
00:00:52,430 --> 00:00:54,350
you haven't eaten or drunk
for three days.

5
00:00:55,150 --> 00:00:56,560
Please, have just a sip.

6
00:00:56,595 --> 00:00:57,808
Even a single mouthful will do.

7
00:00:57,880 --> 00:00:59,520
Silly girl, get up.

8
00:01:00,640 --> 00:01:01,640
If you won't drink,

9
00:01:01,710 --> 00:01:02,640
I won't rise either.

10
00:01:08,040 --> 00:01:09,840
Staying with me
will only bring you hardship.

11
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:11,920
While I still have a say,

12
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:14,350
find yourself a good household.

13
00:01:20,710 --> 00:01:21,630
(Deed of Sale)
Milady,

14
00:01:21,950 --> 00:01:23,680
are you sending me away?

15
00:01:26,230 --> 00:01:27,150
I won't leave.

16
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:29,230
Following me only means suffering.

17
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:31,510
I've set aside travel money for you.

18
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:33,400
Milady,

19
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:36,310
when you were seven,

20
00:01:37,510 --> 00:01:38,870
your mother passed away.

21
00:01:40,040 --> 00:01:42,280
You were trembling in my arms.

22
00:01:43,710 --> 00:01:45,310
We barely made it till morning,

23
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:48,070
and you were struck
by those night terrors.

24
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:50,680
Now, every time you wake up in fear,

25
00:01:51,150 --> 00:01:53,640
you can only hold my hand
to sleep again.

26
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:55,870
Master Huaikang is imprisoned.

27
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:57,840
Even if it costs my life,

28
00:01:58,430 --> 00:02:00,120
I'll die before you, milady.

29
00:02:00,510 --> 00:02:01,430
Silly girl.

30
00:02:02,150 --> 00:02:02,990
Get up now.

31
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:04,950
I'm not sending you away.

32
00:02:09,150 --> 00:02:09,990
Lady Wanyue,

33
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:12,006
Master Huai'an invites you
to the main hall.

34
00:02:13,470 --> 00:02:14,520
Tao,

35
00:02:15,030 --> 00:02:16,150
my lady isn't feeling well.

36
00:02:16,150 --> 00:02:17,160
- Why?
- Can she...

37
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:20,150
Does Jiang Ruoli think
I haven't suffered enough,

38
00:02:20,460 --> 00:02:22,133
so she must find new ways
to humiliate me?

39
00:02:22,870 --> 00:02:23,710
Qiao,

40
00:02:24,150 --> 00:02:24,990
no need to beg her.

41
00:02:25,710 --> 00:02:26,870
I'll go.

42
00:02:27,150 --> 00:02:27,990
Yes.

43
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:36,400
Master, Madam,

44
00:02:36,710 --> 00:02:38,030
Lady Wanyue has arrived.

45
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:40,840
Good.

46
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,520
(What a fine family feast.)

47
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:46,910
(Jiang Ruoli,)

48
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,470
(you wish to drive me mad?)

49
00:02:49,030 --> 00:02:50,840
(I won't let you have your way.)

50
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:55,520
Wanyue is here.

51
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:58,310
Aunt, what does this act mean?

52
00:02:58,750 --> 00:03:00,520
Wanyue, sit down first.

53
00:03:16,150 --> 00:03:18,680
These are your favorite
Jade Shrimp Dumplings.

54
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:21,310
You once fought Yuan for them

55
00:03:22,030 --> 00:03:23,870
and spilled the vinegar dish by mistake.

56
00:03:24,030 --> 00:03:25,150
It stained your new dress.

57
00:03:25,150 --> 00:03:25,990
Isn't that so?

58
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:29,120
(She even remembers such a trifle.)

59
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:30,800
Wanyue,

60
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:34,960
the feud between your father and me
is a matter for the elders.

61
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:37,870
You will always be my niece.

62
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:40,120
You bear the Jiang name.

63
00:03:40,750 --> 00:03:42,150
This family

64
00:03:42,710 --> 00:03:45,120
will forever be your home.

65
00:03:52,150 --> 00:03:53,240
Don't be afraid, Wanyue.

66
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:55,360
This place will always be your home.

67
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:18,400
What is it?

68
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:20,360
Must you snatch food like a child

69
00:04:20,510 --> 00:04:21,430
to find it tasty?

70
00:04:24,270 --> 00:04:25,110
Come on, eat.

71
00:04:27,510 --> 00:04:29,190
Go on, eat up.

72
00:04:34,950 --> 00:04:36,070
Is it good?

73
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:37,200
Yes.

74
00:04:42,270 --> 00:04:43,120
This one's good.

75
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,560
Jiang Ruoli.

76
00:04:51,830 --> 00:04:52,670
Jiang Ruoli,

77
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:55,600
you can humiliate me

78
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:56,630
however you want.

79
00:04:57,070 --> 00:04:59,870
No need to have Uncle and Aunt
act along with you.

80
00:05:01,070 --> 00:05:02,270
Things have come to this,

81
00:05:02,833 --> 00:05:04,033
yet the only thing you can see

82
00:05:04,190 --> 00:05:05,920
is still the small household?

83
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:08,760
Jiang Wanyue,

84
00:05:09,630 --> 00:05:11,750
beyond the inner chambers' strife,

85
00:05:12,310 --> 00:05:14,750
there are far wider places to see.

86
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:16,080
Jiang Ruoli,

87
00:05:16,750 --> 00:05:18,070
easy for you to say.

88
00:05:18,510 --> 00:05:19,920
You're the Chancellor's daughter,

89
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,950
pampered since the day you were born.

90
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:22,890
But I...

91
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:24,680
I've lived only in your shadow,

92
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:25,680
under my father's blows

93
00:05:27,510 --> 00:05:29,750
and cruel words.

94
00:05:30,070 --> 00:05:31,830
All I ever learned was to fight

95
00:05:31,830 --> 00:05:33,430
and to make sure you never had peace.

96
00:05:33,430 --> 00:05:34,560
What else could I have done?

97
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,920
Jiang Huaikang poured his bitterness

98
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:39,310
and failures onto you.

99
00:05:39,630 --> 00:05:40,830
He was weak and cowardly.

100
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:42,750
He was never worthy of being a father.

101
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:44,360
It's not your fault.

102
00:05:47,750 --> 00:05:49,000
In the past, you had no choice.

103
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:50,200
But now,

104
00:05:52,750 --> 00:05:53,830
everything can begin anew.

105
00:05:58,920 --> 00:05:59,760
Wanyue,

106
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,720
this world is vast and boundless.

107
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:06,360
There are countless things
worth a woman's pursuit.

108
00:06:07,510 --> 00:06:08,783
As many as the stars in the sky.

109
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:11,143
As plentiful
as spring bamboo after rain.

110
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:35,640
Mr. Lu,

111
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:36,720
our men have discovered

112
00:06:36,950 --> 00:06:38,870
that Miss Jiang has been investigating

113
00:06:39,190 --> 00:06:40,030
your background.

114
00:06:50,190 --> 00:06:51,030
(As expected,)

115
00:06:52,270 --> 00:06:53,430
(she still remembers.)

116
00:06:53,430 --> 00:06:56,060
(Jiang Mansion)

117
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,070
Yunzhou,

118
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,920
how come you had time to visit today?

119
00:07:09,270 --> 00:07:11,560
My father cleared his name yesterday.

120
00:07:11,606 --> 00:07:13,372
He's been released
from the imperial prison.

121
00:07:14,390 --> 00:07:16,000
Yanzhi is being cared for at home.

122
00:07:16,510 --> 00:07:17,720
I came to tell you

123
00:07:18,190 --> 00:07:19,600
that everything's settled now.

124
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:22,160
Yanzhi won't cause more trouble anymore.

125
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:26,870
That's good to hear.

126
00:07:27,270 --> 00:07:28,110
Yuan,

127
00:07:28,510 --> 00:07:29,600
aren't you curious

128
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:32,920
about how my father cleared his name?

129
00:07:33,750 --> 00:07:36,120
Or do you already know something?

130
00:07:38,390 --> 00:07:39,480
Yunzhou,

131
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,510
what do you mean?

132
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:42,920
How Duke Huo cleared his name

133
00:07:43,070 --> 00:07:44,360
has nothing to do with me.

134
00:07:45,010 --> 00:07:45,870
All I care about

135
00:07:45,870 --> 00:07:48,120
is that my family stays unharmed.

136
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:52,270
You returned with your memories.

137
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:59,680
Why pretend?

138
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:05,000
You're right.

139
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,120
I did come back with my memories.

140
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:10,560
Lu Huaijin,

141
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:12,440
in this lifetime,

142
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,160
every time I see you,

143
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:16,000
I feel utterly disgusted.

144
00:08:17,510 --> 00:08:18,630
Since you already know,

145
00:08:19,950 --> 00:08:21,310
I might as well tell you.

146
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:22,800
Be it the Jiang clan

147
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:25,000
or Yanzhi,

148
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:28,000
whatever you seek to destroy,

149
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:30,190
I will never let it happen.

150
00:08:34,030 --> 00:08:34,870
Good.

151
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,090
Very good.

152
00:08:36,150 --> 00:08:38,630
That's the Yuan I know.

153
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,750
Yuan, you just said

154
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:44,150
I make you feel disgusted.

155
00:08:45,510 --> 00:08:48,870
If Huo Linchuan knew that in seven days,

156
00:08:49,150 --> 00:08:50,150
you'd marry me,

157
00:08:51,670 --> 00:08:52,910
would he be heartbroken?

158
00:08:57,550 --> 00:08:58,480
In your dreams.

159
00:08:58,870 --> 00:08:59,870
In my dreams?

160
00:09:02,270 --> 00:09:05,200
His fate's been sealed in my hands.

161
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:06,790
If you refuse to marry me,

162
00:09:07,510 --> 00:09:08,480
I will curse him

163
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:10,870
never to be reborn.

164
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:12,670
- You...
- Choose.

165
00:09:13,270 --> 00:09:14,360
My dear Yuan,

166
00:09:15,270 --> 00:09:16,720
will you wear the bridal crown

167
00:09:17,790 --> 00:09:19,200
and marry me,

168
00:09:19,550 --> 00:09:22,600
or spend every lifetime apart

169
00:09:23,550 --> 00:09:26,870
from Huo Linchuan?

170
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:27,920
Lu Huaijin.

171
00:09:28,510 --> 00:09:30,080
I hold his fate in my hands.

172
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:31,480
All that he is

173
00:09:37,750 --> 00:09:39,720
lies within my grasp.

174
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:46,600
So what if you love him?

175
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:49,440
Have I ever not been the victor?

176
00:09:50,870 --> 00:09:51,750
In this lifetime,

177
00:09:52,550 --> 00:09:53,910
if you dare run again,

178
00:09:54,790 --> 00:09:56,790
I'll make him live in torment.

179
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:01,160
Watch out!

180
00:10:15,150 --> 00:10:16,000
Fine.

181
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,040
I'll marry you.

182
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,440
But there's one condition.

183
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:25,750
Yanzhi must not be harmed.

184
00:10:25,750 --> 00:10:26,590
Of course.

185
00:10:28,150 --> 00:10:30,120
I want him to see

186
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:31,380
that you and I are the ones

187
00:10:31,790 --> 00:10:34,360
bound by Heaven's will.

188
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:35,920
Yuan,

189
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:38,960
I'll host a feast in the annexe tonight.

190
00:10:39,270 --> 00:10:40,110
Be there

191
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:42,160
or be square.

192
00:11:16,420 --> 00:11:17,940
♪The dream shattered♪

193
00:11:18,300 --> 00:11:19,980
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

194
00:11:19,980 --> 00:11:21,620
♪Like a restless soul♪

195
00:11:22,500 --> 00:11:24,060
♪How vague♪

196
00:11:24,460 --> 00:11:25,980
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

197
00:11:25,980 --> 00:11:28,220
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

198
00:11:29,020 --> 00:11:31,620
♪Love and hate entwined♪

199
00:11:32,100 --> 00:11:34,940
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

200
00:11:35,580 --> 00:11:40,340
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

201
00:11:40,940 --> 00:11:42,460
♪When fate falls apart♪

202
00:11:42,860 --> 00:11:46,420
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

203
00:11:47,140 --> 00:11:48,700
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

204
00:11:49,100 --> 00:11:52,820
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

205
00:11:53,540 --> 00:11:56,380
♪Life after life♪

206
00:11:56,860 --> 00:11:59,540
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

207
00:12:00,180 --> 00:12:04,260
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

208
00:12:04,340 --> 00:12:07,380
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

209
00:12:07,540 --> 00:12:08,940
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

210
00:12:08,940 --> 00:12:12,060
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

211
00:12:12,140 --> 00:12:13,580
♪Now shatter apart♪

212
00:12:13,700 --> 00:12:17,460
♪By fate and karmic ties confined♪

213
00:12:18,180 --> 00:12:20,980
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

214
00:12:21,260 --> 00:12:24,100
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

215
00:12:24,420 --> 00:12:28,820
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

216
00:12:29,060 --> 00:12:31,980
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

217
00:12:32,100 --> 00:12:36,540
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

218
00:12:36,740 --> 00:12:42,460
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

219
00:12:42,900 --> 00:12:45,620
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

220
00:12:45,860 --> 00:12:48,580
♪Sober or indulge♪

221
00:12:49,020 --> 00:12:55,020
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪
